{{other places}} {{Infobox settlement |official_name =Tazehabad |native_name = تازه‌آباد |settlement_type = City |image_skyline = |imagesize = |image_caption = |pushpin_map =Iran |mapsize =150px |subdivision_type = [[List of countries|Country]] |subdivision_name = {{flag|Iran}} |subdivision_type1 =[[Provinces of Iran|Province]] |subdivision_name1 =[[Kermanshah Province|Kermanshah]] |subdivision_type2 =[[Counties of Iran|County]] |subdivision_name2 =[[Salas-e Babajani County|Salas-e Babajani]] |subdivision_type3 =[[Bakhsh]] |subdivision_name3 =[[Central District (Salas-e Babajani County)|Central]] |leader_title = |leader_name = |established_title = |established_date = |area_total_km2 = |area_footnotes = |population_as_of = 2016 Census |population_total =14,701 <ref>https://www.amar.org.ir/english</ref> |population_density_km2 =auto |timezone = [[Iran Standard Time|IRST]] |utc_offset = +3:30 |timezone_DST = [[Iran Daylight Time|IRDT]] |utc_offset_DST = +4:30 |coordinates = {{coord|34|18|51|N|47|04|53|E|region:IR|display=inline,title}} |elevation_m = |website = |area_code = |footnotes = }} '''Tazehabad''' ({{lang-fa|تازه‌آباد}}; also [[Romanize]]d as '''Tāzehābād''')<ref>{{GEOnet3|10117343}}</ref> is a city and capital of [[Salas-e Babajani County]], [[Kermanshah Province]], [[Iran]]. At the 2006 census, its population was 7,479, in 1,661 families.<ref>{{IranCensus2006|05}}</ref>
The spoken language in the city is [[Kurdish language|Kurdish]], but the language which is used in schools and offices is [[Persian language|Persian]], as the official language of [[Iran]] in which almost everyone in the city is fluent.
